title: modify MPM2-generator
body:
I just added a modified version of the mpm2-generator, which allows to further specify the peaks into
1. spheres
2. rotated ellipses
3. non-rotated ellipses.

Actually the python code already allowed that, but the interface had to be modified accordingly. Maybe, this modified version is useful for your package as well - otherwise just ignore this PR :
